  <title>Asmx ve WCF Arasındaki Farklar</title>
  <description>Asmx&amp;nbsp;SOAP ve Http kullanarak mesajlaşabilirken, WCF default olarak Http olmasıyla birlitke TCP/</description>
  <content>&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Asmx&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: red;"&gt;SOAP &lt;/span&gt;ve &lt;span style="color: red;"&gt;Http &lt;/span&gt;kullanarak mesajlaşabilirken, &lt;strong style="font-size: medium;"&gt;WCF&lt;/strong&gt; default olarak Http olmasıyla birlitke &lt;span style="color: red;"&gt;TCP/IP, MSMQ, NamedPipes&lt;/span&gt; etc. gibi yapıları da kullanabilmekte.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Asmx&lt;/strong&gt; servisler sadece &lt;span style="color: red;"&gt;IIS &lt;/span&gt;&amp;uuml;zerinde Host edilebilirken, &lt;strong style="font-size: medium;"&gt;WCF&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: red;"&gt;IIS&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color: red;"&gt;WAS &lt;/span&gt;(Windows Process Activation Services), &lt;span style="color: red;"&gt;Console Application, Windows NT Services &lt;/span&gt;&amp;uuml;zerinde host edilebilmektedir.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Asmx&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;rsquo;de g&amp;uuml;venlik sınırlıdır. Kimlik doğrulama ve yetkilendirme işlemleri &lt;span style="color: red;"&gt;IIS&lt;/span&gt;, &amp;nbsp;&lt;span style="color: red;"&gt;Asp.Net &lt;/span&gt;ve &lt;span style="color: red;"&gt;TCP &lt;/span&gt;Protokol&amp;uuml; kullanılarak yapılır ve kesin bir g&amp;uuml;venlik tutarlılığı yoktur. &lt;strong style="font-size: medium;"&gt;WCF&lt;/strong&gt; her bir protokol i&amp;ccedil;in ayrı bir g&amp;uuml;venlik hizmeti sağlar ve bu y&amp;ouml;nden daha tutarlı bir g&amp;uuml;venlik alt yapısına sahiptir.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Asmx&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;rsquo;de class&amp;rsquo;a &lt;span style="color: red;"&gt;[WebService]&lt;/span&gt; tag&amp;rsquo;i eklenmeliyken, &lt;strong style="font-size: medium;"&gt;WCF&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;rsquo;de class&amp;rsquo;a &lt;span style="color: red;"&gt;[ServiceContract&lt;/span&gt;] tag&amp;rsquo;i eklenmelidir&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: medium;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: medium;"&gt;Asmx&lt;/strong&gt; serilization işlemi i&amp;ccedil;in &lt;span style="color: red;"&gt;XmlSerializer&lt;/span&gt; kullanırken &lt;strong style="font-size: medium;"&gt;WCF&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;XmlSerializer&amp;rsquo;den daha performanslı olan &lt;span style="color: red;"&gt;DataContractSerializer&lt;/span&gt;&amp;rsquo;ı kullanır.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
